data.title: Sodagreen Walk Together Tour live in KL
data.meta_description: Performing for the first time after a short hiatus, popular Taiwanese indie band Sodagreen is back with their 'Walk Together' tour with a stop in KL this March.
data.text: Performing for the first time after a short hiatus, popular Taiwanese indie band Sodagreen is back with their 'Walk Together' tour with a stop in KL this March. Well known for their smooth vocals, poetic lyrics and the unique performing style of vocalist and principle songwriter Wu Tsing-Fong, the six-piece band will be showcasing more than 30 hits from their albums as well as a number of covers.
